shield-drives-2-dc-motors-at-1p2a-per-channel","line":83},{"title":"osepp-motor-servo-shield-v1-drives-2-dc-motors-plus-servos","target":"osepp-motor-servo-shield-v1-drives-2-dc-motors-plus-servos","line":84},{"title":"l298n-dual-h-bridge-motor-driver-drives-2-dc-motors-or-1-stepper-up-to-46v-2a","target":"l298n-dual-h-bridge-motor-driver-drives-2-dc-motors-or-1-stepper-up-to-46v-2a","line":85},{"title":"f130s-small-dc-motor-3-5v-130-can-size","target":"f130s-small-dc-motor-3-5v-130-can-size","line":86},{"title":"arduino-uno-r3-is-a-14-io-5v-board-with-atmega328p-and-usb-b","target":"arduino-uno-r3-is-a-14-io-5v-board-with-atmega328p-and-usb-b","line":87},{"title":"arduino-mega-2560-is-a-54-io-5v-board-with-4-hardware-uarts","target":"arduino-mega-2560-is-a-54-io-5v-board-with-4-hardware-uarts","line":88},{"title":"elegoo-mega-2560-r3-is-an-arduino-mega-clone-with-ch340-usb","target":"elegoo-mega-2560-r3-is-an-arduino-mega-clone-with-ch340-usb","line":89},{"title":"osepp-uno-r3-plus-is-an-arduino-uno-clone-at-5v","target":"osepp-uno-r3-plus-is-an-arduino-uno-clone-at-5v","line":90},{"title":"actuators","target":"actuators","line":93},{"title":"shields","target":"shields","line":94}],"metadata":{"description":"Budget 4-motor shield using L293D — 600mA per channel is enough for small DC motors and the 28BYJ-48 stepper, but don't push it with anything beefier","topics":["[[actuators]]","[[shields]]"],"status":"needs-test","quantity":4,"voltage":[5],"interfaces":["PWM","Digital"],"logic_level":"5V","manufacturer":"DK Electronics","part_number":"HW-130","driver_ic":"L293D","max_current_per_channel":"600mA continuous, 1.2A peak","motor_supply_voltage":"4.5-25V","pinout":"Arduino shield format (stacks on Uno/Mega):\n4 motor channels (M1-M4) via L293D:\n  M1/M2 → L293D chip 1\n  M3/M4 → L293D chip 2\nPWM speed control via Arduino PWM pins\nDirection control via shift register (74HC595)\nServo headers (optional, directly from Arduino PWM pins)\nExternal motor power terminal\n","compatible_with":["[[arduino-uno-r3-is-a-14-io-5v-board-with-atmega328p-and-usb-b]]","[[arduino-mega-2560-is-a-54-io-5v-board-with-4-hardware-uarts]]","[[elegoo-mega-2560-r3-is-an-arduino-mega-clone-with-ch340-usb]]","[[osepp-uno-r3-plus-is-an-arduino-uno-clone-at-5v]]"],"used_in":[],"warnings":["600mA per channel is the hard limit — most DC motors stall above this","Some clones use counterfeit L293D chips with even lower current ratings","Uses many Arduino pins — check which pins are consumed before stacking other shields"],"datasheet_url":""},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:docs/parts/dk-electronics-hw-130-motor-shield-uses-l293d-at-600ma.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"xslwyx","at":1776152925099},"key":"docs/parts/dk-electronics-hw-130-motor-shield-uses-l293d-at-600ma.md#---frontmatter---","lines":[1,27],"size":1338,"outlinks":[{"title":"actuators","target":"actuators","line":3},{"title":"shields","target":"shields","line":3},{"title":"arduino-mega-2560-is-a-54-io-5v-board-with-4-hardware-uarts","target":"arduino-mega-2560-is-a-54-io-5v-board-with-4-hardware-uarts","line":23},{"title":"arduino-uno-r3-is-a-14-io-5v-board-with-atmega328p-and-usb-b","target":"arduino-uno-r3-is-a-14-io-5v-board-with-atmega328p-and-usb-b","line":23},{"title":"elegoo-mega-2560-r3-is-an-arduino-mega-clone-with-ch340-usb","target":"elegoo-mega-2560-r3-is-an-arduino-mega-clone-with-ch340-usb","line":23},{"title":"osepp-uno-r3-plus-is-an-arduino-uno-clone-at-5v","target":"osepp-uno-r3-plus-is-an-arduino-uno-clone-at-5v","line":23}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
